          "settings": {
            "content": "<h3>Sheet Sets & Pillowcases</h3><p><strong>100% Eucalyptus Lyocell</strong> - Woven in a percale style for maximum breathability and crisp feel. Thread count optimized for durability and comfort rather than just numbers.</p><h3>Comforters & Duvets</h3><p><strong>Shell:</strong> 100% Eucalyptus Lyocell for temperature regulation<br><strong>Fill:</strong> Down alternative clusters made from recycled polyester for loft without weight<br><strong>Construction:</strong> Baffle box design prevents fill shifting</p><h3>Loungewear</h3><p><strong>Eucalyptus Modal Blend:</strong> 95% Modal, 5% Spandex for stretch and recovery. Modal provides drape and softness while spandex adds flexibility for movement.</p><h3>Pillows</h3><p><strong>Memory Foam:</strong> CertiPUR-US certified foam free from harmful chemicals<br><strong>Cover:</strong> 100% Eucalyptus Lyocell for cooling and breathability<br><strong>Design:</strong> Ventilation channels for enhanced airflow</p>"
